People are getting slow speeds because of anti-peer-to-peer efforts by HBO. They hire companies to create fake seeders that only serve you incorrect data and then send you a cease and desist letter. When there's a torrent with a ridiculously large number of seeders it's usually because of this activity. Just use PeerBlock and your speeds will be fine, plus no C&D letter.
